    "# Task-Aware Sparse YOLO — Stage 2 Simulation\n",
    "**DVCon India 2026 | Submission #51**  \n",
    "Rhythm Patel & Nikhil Patel | SVNIT Surat\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### What this notebook does\n",
    "| Step | Module | Output |\n",
    "|------|--------|--------|\n",
    "| 1 | Setup & install | Dependencies ready |\n",
    "| 2 | COCO task definitions | 14 tasks mapped to class IDs |\n",
    "| 3 | YOLOv5-nano inference | Raw detections on COCO val images |\n",
    "| 4 | Activation sparsity | Per-layer sparsity %, MAC reduction % |\n",
    "| 5 | DistilBERT encoder | Task embeddings + encoding latency |\n",
    "| 6 | Cross-modal fusion | Task-filtered detections, suppression rate |\n",
    "| 7 | Latency comparison | Sequential vs pipelined, speedup factor |\n",
    "| 8 | Result plots | 7 publication-ready figures |\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Runtime:** Set to `T4 GPU` → Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU"
